{"tid":2489200,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟一支啤酒，宣稱0酒精，咁仲係咪啤酒？","createTime":"2021-04-14T20:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T06:20:14.000Z","uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"06be0c6fbd6a100fe29a293253a31b929509139f","tid":2489200,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T20:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定只不過係碳酸水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c33fd376986b262b94367b737e012297195cc5","tid":2489200,"uid":193476,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T20:22:54.000Z","msg":"啤酒既定義係有酒精飲料<br />\n無酒精就只可以叫做碳酸飲料"},{"pid":"4238d45a8afa0a3399d966650080538e5840e094","tid":2489200,"uid":374806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T20:22:59.000Z","msg":"其實都係睇你對啤酒嘅定義係點啫<br />\n<br />\n利申之前嘉士伯啱啱出咗隻藍色罐無酒精啤酒，貪新鮮買咗罐黎飲，飲咗兩啖就頂唔順倒咗，真係好撚難飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cca0d7b7758163af9dfe39e68f9073d9c8c833","tid":2489200,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:43:04.000Z","msg":"如果用香港嘅定義，只能叫「麥汁風味通力水(Tonic water)」，<br />\n唔能夠稱作「啤酒風味汽水」(因為有「酒」字，會引致誤會或招致判罰風險) <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959a30876c741afa42f96551e0d1635e1960b3fc","tid":2489200,"uid":267447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T01:51:49.000Z","msg":"如果係第二種製法<br />\n其實算係啤酒減少酒精<br />\n咁應該都係啤酒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//無酒精啤酒的製作方法<br />\n<br />\n傳統的啤酒的製程是將麥芽搗碎、糖化與煮沸後製成的麥芽汁，加入酵母進行發酵反應，產生酒精與迷人的氣泡。無酒精啤酒的製作方法，則可分為數種：<br />\n<br />\n1、使用傳統方法與原料製作啤酒，再以減壓蒸餾或者膜過濾的加工方式，把酒精與啤酒液體分離。這個方法雖然可以將成份中的酒精分離，但同時也會使得發酵的風味喪失，因此業界目前未採用這個方法。<br />\n<br />\n2、<span class=\"red\"><strong>以傳統的方法製作啤酒，並以製程調整的方式，控制酒精的含量。像是利用控制釀造時的糖分的含量，限制酵母生產出酒精；使用能夠創造風味，但產酒精量極低的菌株來進行發酵；又或者在釀製完成後，以約40－50&deg;C的溫度加熱去除啤酒中的酒精。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n3、使用麥芽汁做為原料，不進行酒精發酵，以其他的加工方式與添加物（如添加二氧化碳等方式），讓產品能擁有類似啤酒的口感與風味。//<br />\n<br />\n醬油：<a href=\"https://www.foodnext.net/science/machining/paper/4616185666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodnext.net%2Fscience%2Fmachining%2Fpaper%2F4616185666&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=8a64e14e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foodnext.net/science/machining/paper/4616185666</a>"},{"pid":"3614498aeb2587b2d74a8cb3a96fdc6e253c6481","tid":2489200,"uid":10157,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:03:00.000Z","msg":"都唔明點解d人會飲無酒精啤<br />\n根本垃圾產品黎<br />\n要無酒精不如飲汽水"},{"pid":"0353b86ef068c1ffadf870ac1ca0ff8da3628de8","tid":2489200,"uid":99828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:04:03.000Z","msg":"咁薑啤呢"},{"pid":"741e8b98cfef023ff322dd7beab5e9440db582d6","tid":2489200,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:06:42.000Z","msg":"你當佢係有麥芽苦味嘅汽水, 心理上會好過啲"},{"pid":"06533aba8b6f8ace5b6d78c40dd73f20f8d94e4f","tid":2489200,"uid":238214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3614498aeb2587b2d74a8cb3a96fdc6e253c6481","tid":2489200,"uid":10157,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:03:00.000Z","msg":"都唔明點解d人會飲無酒精啤<br />\n根本垃圾產品黎<br />\n要無酒精不如飲汽水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"要減肥/其他慢性病(糖尿病之類)  唔飲得酒 又想過下癮"},{"pid":"3395d1dc0a2a985e42c9fedac57a6c304ef5aeaf","tid":2489200,"uid":155319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"酒精含量唔多過1.2%就唔叫酒精飲品<br />\n其實市面上既無酒精啤酒都會有大概0.5%左右既酒精<br />\n同你食條熟蕉冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e362e537be6e56370baf128f3390207a96ebf2","tid":2489200,"uid":163632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:54:55.000Z","msg":"其實唔係0酒精，你當jolly shandy咁"},{"pid":"6b42b199e1a3e9c2b4669d024f6dd6269f5dad7f","tid":2489200,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4238d45a8afa0a3399d966650080538e5840e094","tid":2489200,"uid":374806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T20:22:59.000Z","msg":"其實都係睇你對啤酒嘅定義係點啫<br />\n<br />\n利申之前嘉士伯啱啱出咗隻藍色罐無酒精啤酒，貪新鮮買咗罐黎飲，飲咗兩啖就頂唔順倒咗，真係好撚難飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"呢款要買玻璃樽<br />\n仲有買完擺一個月+雪凍<br />\n嗰浸啤酒味先會出嚟<br />\n<br />\n買完即刻飲會好淡味"},{"pid":"786af493465fcb67b0c972e9a48225ecdef4086e","tid":2489200,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06be0c6fbd6a100fe29a293253a31b929509139f","tid":2489200,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T20:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定只不過係碳酸水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"0 酒精難飲到仆晒街<br />\n<br />\n飲兩啖就已經要拋落垃圾筒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"